data.description: Beautiful home located in the much sought after Savannah Pointe neighborhood.  Enter the home to a large foyer leading to an open dining and great room area.  Large great room features a vaulted ceiling and wood. burning fireplace.  Spacious dining room with custom molding.  Eat in kitchen is nice sized and has built in microwave and matching appliances.  Split bedroom plan.  Master bedroom features a trey ceiling, walk in closet and huge bath with double vanity, garden tub and separate shower.  Scratch-proof LVP flooring in the foyer, den, dining room and kitchen. New roof (installed in January 2022).  Savannah Pointe is a clubhouse, tennis court and swimming pool community.  This home is only a few miles from the interstate and convenient to shopping and local schools.  Don't miss your opportunity to own this lovely home.
